OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,FITV News Entertainment Reporter Rishi
OL,7,FDavda looks back at the life and
OL,8,Flegacy of fashion designer Valentino,
OL,9,Ffollowing his death at the age of 93
OL,11,FValentino Garavani, the jet-set
OL,12,FItalian designer, has died at home in
OL,13,FRome, his foundation announced Monday.
OL,14,FHe was 93.
OL,16,F"Valentino Garavani was not only a
OL,17,Fconstant guide and inspiration for all
OL,18,Fof us, but a true source of light,
OL,19,Fcreativity and vision, the foundation
OL,20,Fsaid in a statement posted on social
OL,21,Fmedia.
