OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,FHis body will repose at the
OL,7,Ffoundation's headquarters in Rome on
OL,8,FWednesday and Thursday. The funeral
OL,9,Fwill be held Friday at the Basilica
OL,10,FSanta Maria degli Angeli e dei Martiri
OL,11,Fin Rome's Piazza della Repubblica.
OL,13,FUniversally known by his first name,
OL,14,FValentino was adored by generations of
OL,15,Froyals, first ladies and movie stars,
OL,16,Ffrom Jackie Kennedy Onassis to Julia
OL,17,FRoberts and Queen Rania of Jordan, who
OL,18,Fswore the designer always made them
OL,19,Flook and feel their best.
