OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,F"I know what women want," he once
OL,7,Fremarked. "They want to be beautiful."
OL,9,FHis fail-safe designs made Valentino
OL,10,Fthe king of the red carpet, the go-to
OL,11,Fman for A-listers' awards ceremony
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,FHis sumptuous gowns have graced
OL,15,Fcountless Academy Awards, notably in
OL,16,F2001, when Roberts wore a vintage
OL,17,Fblack and white column to accept her
OL,18,Fbest actress statue.
