OL,6,FValentino was also behind the long-
OL,7,Fsleeved lace dress Jacqueline Kennedy
OL,8,Fwore for her wedding to Greek shipping
OL,9,Fmagnate Aristotle Onassis in 1968.
OL,11,FHe was also close to Diana, Princess
OL,12,Fof Wales, who often donned his
OL,13,Fsumptuous gowns.
