OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,FPerpetually tanned and always
OL,7,Fimpeccably dressed, Valentino shared
OL,8,Fthe lifestyle of his jet-set patrons.
OL,9,FIn addition to his 152-foot (46-meter)
OL,10,Fyacht and an art collection including
OL,11,Fworks by Picasso and Miro, the
OL,12,Fcouturier owned a 17th-century chateau
OL,13,Fnear Paris with a garden said to boast
OL,14,Fmore than a million roses.
