OL,7,FGiancarlo Giammetti flitted among
OL,8,Ftheir homes ` which also included
OL,9,Fplaces in New York, London, Rome,
OL,10,FCapri and Gstaad, Switzerland `
OL,11,Ftraveling with their pack of pugs. The
OL,12,Fpair regularly received A-list friends
OL,13,Fand patrons, including Madonna and
OL,14,FGwyneth Paltrow.
