OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,FValentino was born into a well-off
OL,7,Ffamily in the northern Italian town of
OL,8,FVoghera on May 11, 1932. He said it
OL,9,Fwas his childhood love of cinema that
OL,10,Fset him down the fashion path.
OL,12,F"I was crazy for silver screen, I was
OL,13,Fcrazy for beauty, to see all those
OL,14,Fmovie stars being sensation, well
OL,15,Fdressed, being always perfect," he
OL,16,Fexplained in the 2007 television
OL,17,Finterview.
