OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Valentino
OL,4,Cdies aged 93
OL,6,FAfter studying fashion in Milan and
OL,7,FParis, he spent much of the 1950s
OL,8,Fworking for established Paris-based
OL,9,Fdesigner Jean Desses and later Guy
OL,10,FLaroche before striking out on his
OL,11,Fown. He founded the house of Valentino
OL,12,Fon Rome's Via Condotti in 1959.
OL,14,FFrom the beginning, Giammetti was by
OL,15,Fhis side, handling the business aspect
OL,16,Fwhile Valentino used his natural charm
OL,17,Fto build a client base among the
OL,18,Fworld's rich and fabulous.
