OL,6,FAfter some early financial setbacks `
OL,7,FValentino's tastes were always lavish,
OL,8,Fand the company spent with abandon `
OL,9,Fthe brand took off.
OL,11,FEarly fans included Italian screen
OL,12,Fsirens Gina Lollobrigida and Sophia
OL,13,FLoren, as well as Hollywood stars
OL,14,FElizabeth Taylor and Audrey Hepburn.
OL,15,FLegendary American Vogue editor-in-
OL,16,Fchief Diana Vreeland also took the
OL,17,Fyoung designer under her wing.
