OL,6,FOver the years, Valentino's empire
OL,7,Fexpanded as the designer added ready-
OL,8,Fto-wear, menswear and accessories
OL,9,Flines to his stable. Valentino and
OL,10,FGiammetti sold the label to an Italian
OL,11,Fholding company for an estimated $300
OL,12,Fmillion in 1998. Valentino would
OL,13,Fremain in a design role for another
OL,14,Fdecade.
